title: Roquan Smith traded to Ravens! (Emergency Pod)
itunes:title: Roquan Smith traded to Ravens! (Emergency Pod)
description:
A virtual room filled with some heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, and Gregg Rosenthal react to the breaking news that Roquan Smith has been traded from the Chicago Bears to the Baltimore Ravens. What does this mean for the Ravens' chances to compete for a Super Bowl? What is the plan in Chicago? The heroes discuss the impacts of this move as the trade deadline looms...

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
